text:
🍁🍂Jering Trail is another wooden boardwalk set above the reservior's water.
🍂Walk comfortably along this short trail and take in sight of the tranquil calm waters.
Feel the occasional breeze and the rustling of the tree leaves.
🍂As you leave Jering Trail, you have the option to go further by taking the Golf Link, or to return either by Lornie Trail or by the very same Jering Trail.
